Paper: hep-th/9910029

Date: 1999-10-04

Title: Covariant formulation of non-Abelian gauge theories without

anticommuting variablesAuthors: A.A.Slavnov

Comments: 8 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B469 (1999) 155-160

A manifestly Lorentz invariant effective action for Yang-Mills theorydepending only on commuting fields is constructed. This action posesses abosonic symmetry, which plays a role analogous to the BRST symmetry in thestandard formalism.